BrightBlade, Rage

* BrightBlade watched from her vantage point as another bot came onto the 
scene, it was some sort of squid or something like that.
She smiled and whispered into her comlink...*

" Hay! Gangon! Maybe we'll get a little show before we have to kick some 
traitor butt!"

* She closed her comlink and smiled as she loaded her gun, this may be 
good!*

^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

* Rage roared in protest as she saw her prey slip into the metal structure, 
she snarled.
Her stomach complained, it had looked forward to being full again!
Rage had moved off considerably when she say another raptor come from the 
metal thing but knew better then to bite into one of those again, second she 
saw something fast speed away from the same thing and off into the distance. 
She was so hungry!
Soon she had her mind set on only one thing and her thoughts echoed in her 
head...*

< Food!> <Eat!> <Food!!!>
